tedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:37:09.000Z","msg":"占星學應該仲有相位、宮位、搖籃果類概念，應該冇辦法咁淺層分析"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"喺個Excel開多幾個column囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T17:01:22.000Z","msg":"人人出生嘅時間都唔同wor"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"咁咪輸入出生時間囉，有咩問題？"},{"pid":"cd7448ae63f9b7c0c951c9cbe35e465f6300c037","tid":2205650,"uid":71237,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"42c9e3c98891b38cb7b82e9a0e2576e2c1a0b24f","tid":2205650,"uid":192893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"340292a3c3fdd8dadeac5dc38da67a8c0d536072","tid":2205650,"uid":71237,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"362bbdf3190dc87728accd464c7d813d3c923c9d","tid":2205650,"uid":192893,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"首先你要知道統計學係對一樣嘢嘅原理唔夠了解先會用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:43:44.000Z","msg":"係啲星座大師自己話星座係統計學嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:47:26.000Z","msg":"佛洛伊德會睇星座, 咁星座係咪精神分析學?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T17:34:02.000Z","msg":"唔太清楚巴打你想表達啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n星座大師聲稱自己運用咗統計學，甚至指星座就係統計學，但其實佢地從來都無運用到統計學。<br />\n如果你想舉例子，應該用返一個「某人聲稱有運用某學說，但其實無運用到」或者「聲聲A學說就係B學說」嘅例子。<br />\n<br />\n佛洛伊德會睇星座，但係佢無聲稱星座係精神分析。<br />\n天文台會運用統計學預測天氣，但唔代表天文台淨係用統計學預測天氣，佢都要結合其他物理學、地理學知識去作出預測。佢地亦都無表示天氣預報就係統計學。"},{"pid":"0b2255d47511cbc6ddd8a18e3ca47ee16a9a6d67","tid":2205650,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4de4257017fafd6ff5e2685aafe49c14bbd30c0","tid":2205650,"uid":364916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:51:46.000Z","msg":"性格實在太抽象<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無乜評估標準"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T17:40:28.000Z","msg":"要請教星座大師"},{"pid":"38fff7dfdbf4d180801cf9d2a6573f6dd0f58587","tid":2205650,"uid":298578,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fc0f8a441e1be78587421afcf9595ca60478032f","tid":2205650,"uid":71237,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"45c284faa02e59445fe0872779dde0ff4361f60e","tid":2205650,"uid":88663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:49:24.000Z","msg":"以雙子座做例子， sample size幾大先最代表性？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:04:00.000Z","msg":"其實答案係出奇地細。<br />\n睇吓你要幾準，同埋你個population有幾大，網上有calculator可以計需要幾大嘅sample size。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.surveysystem.com/sscalc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.surveysystem.com%2Fsscalc.htm&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=76a33362\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.surveysystem.com/sscalc.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n全球人口我當70億左右，假設雙子座嘅人佔1/12，都有5.83億人。<br />\n例如我想估計雙子座嘅人當中，有幾多%係信星座。<br />\n其實我只需要抽9604人，就已經有95%肯定真正答案喺正負1%之內。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T17:54:19.000Z","msg":"咪傻啦佢地有星盤同日月星座出生年月日做後備架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好諗住用理據同佢講野,你會輸"},{"pid":"2e1da3827da203a96b5212f192e9df9efe925816","tid":2205650,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T18:43:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ba82d82734d149123399121604859c2da2ea672","tid":2205650,"uid":201822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deb5fb41325b65a2d8da38eb6d7b1af0de2cec64","tid":2205650,"uid":71237,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:33:27.000Z","msg":"想入行做星座大師應該學R定Python？好似唔覺佢地有library專門for星座分析。<br />\n想問吓各位星座大師用開邊種程式語言？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T18:50:11.000Z","msg":"用colab<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df10f8ee5bf552ceb81283af83d11951179a9fb8","tid":2205650,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T18:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434a782b0a6e2787ac9357921ca9fa69d4aa4f21","tid":2205650,"uid":41243,"like":1,"dislik